summary: This code defines the "AppDelegate" class, which inherits from UIResponder and adopts the UIApplicationDelegate protocol. It includes properties for a window, NVView, HeLogView, TOMVision2, and an integer for bird birth position mode. The class also provides three methods: getTopDisplayViewController, setTipLog, and setNoLogMode.
